                  <msItem class="#proverbia #oratio #theologica">
                     <note>On fols. ii verso, iii recto are some <title key="work_15283" type="desc">theological notes</title> in Latin, an English <title key="work_14061" type="desc">proverb</title>, and a French prayer, and on fol. iii verso some Latin notes of papal indulgences, etc.: some rude figures of a captive and redeemed soul are on fol. 72v: and a cryptic note or name on fol. 172v.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="la" otherLangs="enm xno">Latin, Middle English and Anglo-Norman</textLang>
